title: Jankovic, Stosur advance to quarterfinals at Hong Kong Open
text:
Kin Cheung Jankovic, Stosur advance to quarterfinals at Hong Kong Open 
Samantha Stosur of Australia returns a shot against Monica Puig of Puerto Rica during the second round match at the WTA Hong Kong Open tennis tournament in Hong Kong, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015. (AP Photo/Kin Cheung) Kin Cheung Jankovic, Stosur advance to quarterfinals at Hong Kong Open 
Monica Puig of Puerto Rica hits a return shot against Samantha Stosur of Australia during the second round match at the WTA Hong Kong Open tennis tournament in Hong Kong, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015. (AP Photo/Kin Cheung) Posted: Wednesday, October 14, 2015 5:02 am Jankovic, Stosur advance to quarterfinals at Hong Kong Open Associated Press | 
HONG KONG (AP) â€” Jelena Jankovic and Samantha Stosur advanced to the quarterfinals of the Hong Kong Open on Wednesday, both winning in straight sets. 
Jankovic, a former top-ranked player from Serbia, beat Anastasia Rodionova of Australia 6-0, 6-2. Stosur defeated Monica Puig of Puerto Rico 6-4, 6-4. Subscription Required An online service is needed to view this article in its entirety. You
